The '''China Institute of Atomic Energy''' ('''CIAE''') is the main research institute of the [[China National Nuclear Corporation]] (CNNC).<ref>{{cite web|title=Research Institutions|url=http://en.cnnc.com.cn/institutions.html|website=en.cnnc.com.cn|accessdate=3 March 2017|language=en}}</ref><ref name=nti />
Founded in 1950, it conducts research in the fields of [[nuclear physics]], [[nuclear engineering]], [[radiochemistry]], and in the development of nuclear technology.<ref name=nti>{{cite web|title=China Institute of Atomic Energy (CIAE) {{!}} Facilities  {{!}} NTI|url=http://www.nti.org/learn/facilities/700/|website=www.nti.org|accessdate=3 March 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=CIAE|url=http://www.ciae.ac.cn/eng/CIAE/index.htm|website=www.ciae.ac.cn|accessdate=3 March 2017}}</ref>

